doctype html
html(lang='en')
    head 
        meta(http-equiv='Content-Type' content='text/html; charset=UTF-8')
        meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge')
        title (c)ypher
        meta(name='description', content='This website is created by and for the tech club of DPS Bhopal - Team (c)ypher.')
        meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
        link(rel="shortcut icon" href="/img/cypher.png?v=1" type="image/x-icon")
        link(rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css")
    body
        header
            .logo
                a.handletter(href='/home')
                    img(src='/img/cync_logo-converted.png' cursor-class='arrow' alt='cync')
            img.mob-logo(src='/img/cync_logo-converted.png' cursor-class='arrow' alt='cync')
            #mobilenavdiv.mobile-menu-toggle.js-toggle-menu.hamburger-menu(onclick='navfunction()')
                span.menu-item
                span.menu-item
                span.menu-item
            nav.navbar.desktop-nav
                if currentUser
                    ul
                        li
                            a(href='/home' cursor-class='arrow') Home
                        li
                            a(href='/events' cursor-class='arrow') Events
                        li
                            a(href='/dashboard' cursor-class='arrow') Dashboard
                        li
                            a(href='/logout' cursor-class='arrow') Logout from #{currentUser.username}
                else
                    ul
                        li
                            a(href='/home' cursor-class='arrow') Home
                        li
                            a(href='/events' cursor-class='arrow') Events
                        li
                            a(href='/login' cursor-class='arrow') Login
                        li
                            a(href='/register' cursor-class='arrow') Register
            nav#nav.mobile-nav.hidden
                if currentUser
                    ul
                        li
                            a(href='/home' cursor-class='arrow') Home
                        li
                            a(href='/events' cursor-class='arrow') Events
                        li
                            a(href='/dashboard' cursor-class='arrow') Dashboard
                        li
                            a(href='/logout' cursor-class='arrow') Logout
                else
                    ul
                        li
                            a(href='/home' cursor-class='arrow') Home
                        li
                            a(href='/events' cursor-class='arrow') Events
                        li
                            a(href='/login' cursor-class='arrow') Login
                        li
                            a(href='/register' cursor-class='arrow') Register
        #canvas
        #main
            section.landing
                #cursor
                    .cursor__circle
                .left
                    .text
                        h1(cursor-class='arrow') Doing The Impossible
                        p(cursor-class='arrow')
                            | We at 
                            span (c)ypher
                            |  believe that a piece of code is mightier
                            |             than a pen as well as a sword. We are a team, excelling in various
                            |             fields such as 
                            span computer programming
                            |  ,
                            span web development
                            | ,
                            span photo and video editing
                            |  etc. We fascinate people by our
                            |             creations, and draw people to the magnificent and unexplored world
                            |             of computers.
                        br
                        .btn-landing
                            a.btn(href='/register') Register
                .right
                    .timer
                        .row
                            .container-day(cursor-class='timerCursor')
                                h3.day Time
                                h3 Days
                            .container-hour(cursor-class='timerCursor')
                                h3.hour Time
                                h3 Hours
                        .row
                            .container-minute(cursor-class='timerCursor')
                                h3.minute Time
                                h3 Minutes
                            .container-second(cursor-class='timerCursor')
                                h3.second Time
                                h3 Seconds
            section.cync
                .left-cync
                    .left-box
                        p.logo-p (c)
                        .logo-text
                            p
                            | Started in Fall 2014, (c)ync is an initiative by (c)lub (c)ypher
                            | to celebrate and promote the spirit of technology and human
                            | intelligence.
                .right-cync
                    .right-box
                        p
                            | (c)ync v1.0 to (c)ync v6.0 were grand success and people are
                            | expecting its next version. (c)ync is one of its kind in our city
                            | Bhopal and will encourage other schools to be a part of it.
                        br
                        p
                            | We&rsquo;re organizing our annual IT symposium, (c)ync v6, on July 27,
                            | 2019. (c)ync v6 is an exclusive invite-only event, with the
                            | exception of De(c)ypher, and invites are extended to a select number
                            | of the very best schools in Bhopal, based on significant
                            | achievements in the previous years. The event will consist of our
                            | online hunt,
                            a.event-btn(href='https://www.clubcypher.club/' target='_blank') De(c)ypher
                            |             , 
                            a.event-btn(href='#') (C)rosshair
                            | ,
                            a.event-btn(href='#')  (C)lick
                            | , and
                            a.event-btn(href='#')  (C)lipped
                            | .
            footer
                .imp-links
                    .left-footer
                        h2
                            | (c)ync will be held on 2nd of August. All events will be conducted on the internet.
                        br
                        p
                            | For any further queries, please contact Mr. Anurag Sehgal: +91
                            | 7869119509
                        p
                            | The results will be declared on 11th of August. See you there!
                    .right-footer
                        h2 More Links
                        .links
                            .right1
                                ul
                                    li
                                        a(href='/events') Events
                                    li
                                        a(href='/register') Register
                                    li
                                        a(href='/login') Login
                            .right2
                                ul
                                    li
                                        a(href='https://www.instagram.com/cypherdps/' target='_blank') Instagram
                                    li
                                        a(href='#' target='_blank') Discord
                                    li
                                        a(href='#' target='_blank') YouTube
                .last
                    p With &#x1F497; from (c)lub (c)ypher
            script(src='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/three.js/r77/three.min.js')
            script(type='module' src='/js/index.js')
            script.
                function navfunction() {
                    document.getElementsByClassName('js-toggle-menu')[0].classList.toggle('open');
                    document.getElementById("main").classList.toggle('temp-body')
                    document.getElementsByClassName("hidden")[0].classList.toggle("notHidden")
                };

